# PC Security Check 

This repository helps you check your PC for viruses and other threats safely.

## Windows
1. Open **Windows Security**:
   - Search for "Windows Security" in Start menu.
   - Go to **Virus & threat protection** → **Quick scan**.
2. Use **Microsoft Safety Scanner** (optional, more thorough):
   - Download: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/intelligence/safety-scanner-download
   - Run the tool and follow instructions.

## Mac
1. Check **built-in protection**:
   - Go to **System Settings → Privacy & Security → Security settings**.
   - Ensure firewall is enabled.
2. Use **Malwarebytes for Mac** (optional):
   - Download: https://www.malwarebytes.com/mac
   - Run scan and remove threats if found.

## Recommended Best Practices
- Keep your system updated.
- Avoid suspicious downloads.
- Backup important files regularly.

